 a Tor over VPN server), eight servers in Taiwan, and nearly 1,000 servers in over 50 countries around the world.<br />\n<br />\nProtonVPN間公司個CEO係台灣人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2027338/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2027338/page/1</a><br />\n家族來自台灣台南的嚴育銓（Andy Yen），人生的第一次創業選擇了瑞士──他與團隊打造的加密電子郵件系統「ProtonMail」，2016年正式問世，<span style=\"color: red;\">不到4年，使用者就超越了2,000多萬人，包括許多國家機器容不下的異議者、記者、流亡者；這讓嚴育詮成了中國與俄羅斯等極權政府的眼中釘，同時引起稱霸全球搜尋和電子郵件的Google注意。</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：我未用過 依加down黎用<br />\n無錢 無時間 唔識搞 唔係借口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗錢仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地開到口支持香港 <br />\n未有vpn既你拿拿臨裝左先 全民vpn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nApple: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/protonvpn-fast-secure-vpn/id1437005085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fprotonvpn-fast-secure-vpn%2Fid1437005085&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3gAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=c51e8799\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/us/app/protonvpn-fast-secure-vpn/id1437005085</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ch.protonvpn.android&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dch.protonvpn.android%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3gAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=4da3216d\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ch.protonvpn.android&amp;hl=zh_HK</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"好用嗎 ?"},{"pid":"795a6024cff73ed64e62829ebc6429093ae10ec0","tid":2034650,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b53240c1b6a1976a533f74c9d59166a36aa52fcc","tid":2034650,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"459ca79a97c9c77152c240ee51b7925a036917ea","tid":2034650,"uid":51142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"